'''Nala trees''' were presumably the staple of [[nala tree frog]]s. They were bulbous in appearance and thrived on the tropical [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Ylesia/Legends|Ylesia]]. Additionally, the [[Tree/Legends|trees]] were quintessential means for hiding used by [[Slavery/Legends|slaves]] escaping the depressive rule of the [[Besadii/Legends|Besadii]] [[Hutt/Legends|Hutts]].

